---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About — Joy4Wine | Wine in Málaga"
  description="About Joy4Wine — a personal guide to wine shops, wineries, and bottles in Málaga and the Costa del Sol."
>
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <h1>About Joy4Wine</h1>
      <p>A personal guide to wine in Málaga and the Costa del Sol.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container--narrow prose" style="max-width:65ch; margin:0 auto; padding-inline:1.5rem;">
      <p>
        I recently moved to Málaga and started exploring the wine scene across the Costa del Sol.
        There are great wine shops, local producers, tasting experiences and regional bottles to
        discover — but clear, practical information in English can be hard to find.
      </p>
      <p>
        Joy4Wine is my personal guide to that discovery: wine shops, wineries, bottles, tasting
        ideas and local observations from Málaga and beyond. It is written mainly for international
        residents and visitors, but also for locals who enjoy seeing the wine scene through a
        slightly different lens.
      </p>
      <p>
        Everything here is written from personal experience — visits, tastings, and direct
        encounters with the local wine scene. I don't accept advertising, freebies, or payment
        for coverage. The opinions are entirely my own.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you find something useful here, or if you'd like to recommend a wine shop or producer
        I should visit, I'd love to hear from you. You can find me on Instagram at
        <a href="https://instagram.com/joy.4.wine" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@joy.4.wine</a>.
      </p>
      <hr style="border:none; border-top:1px solid var(--color-border); margin:2.5rem 0;" />
      <p class="credential" style="font-size:0.875rem; color:var(--color-text-muted); font-style:italic;">
        Written by a Málaga-based wine enthusiast currently working towards the WSET Diploma.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
